  "detailed_description": "<h1>SUPPORTED CONTROLLERS</h1><p>Scrash is a local Player VS Player game that requires 2 controllers (battle tested on PS4 and Xbox 360/One controllers)</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1>Scrash is the ultimate couch face-off. Players must battle to take control of the ball, breakout obstacles and score goals.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SEIZE the ball or STEAL it from your opponent</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/25343f11b57225ffd7607e3c07cc50cc.poster.avif?t=1530396636\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/25343f11b57225ffd7607e3c07cc50cc.webm?t=1530396636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/25343f11b57225ffd7607e3c07cc50cc.mp4?t=1530396636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Each individual level brings a set rules with challenging arenas. In some matches, the objective is to hit the opponent with a speeding ball, whereas others may feature colored goals, breakable blocks, volleyball nets and more.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MOVE fast and BREAK obstacles</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/5540da125f6839347f8f1653ac22bd32.poster.avif?t=1530396636\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/5540da125f6839347f8f1653ac22bd32.webm?t=1530396636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/5540da125f6839347f8f1653ac22bd32.mp4?t=1530396636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>A new level is loaded with each score, making matches as long as skills permit and as short as a blink. Wins the player with the highest score when the other yields... In shame.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SCORE amazing goals and BRAG about your skills</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/c38541d6bb28eb26a5264cb1c46b18e8.poster.avif?t=1530396636\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/c38541d6bb28eb26a5264cb1c46b18e8.webm?t=1530396636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/c38541d6bb28eb26a5264cb1c46b18e8.mp4?t=1530396636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Scrash is a new take on the classic arcade genre, bringing elements from the early videogame era. A tribute to breakable obstacles, air hockey and table-tennis all in one.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OBLITERATE adversaries in DUELS to the death</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/becfd2f56c330b108e3d57013852c7b2.poster.avif?t=1530396636\" width=512 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/becfd2f56c330b108e3d57013852c7b2.webm?t=1530396636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/becfd2f56c330b108e3d57013852c7b2.mp4?t=1530396636\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HOW to PLAY</h2>To play Scrash, you need 2 controllers (PS4 or Xbox, preferably) and a friend.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/807050/extras/f28f709d381228e1d286bfa255f9f5c4.avif?t=1530396636\" width=616 height=214 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >KEY FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Free <br></li><li>Local multiplayer party-game<br></li><li>No characters, no plot holes, no narrative <br></li><li>Responsive, tight and fast-paced gameplay<br></li><li>7 Tailor-made levels to ensure the best experience after each score<br></li><li>Quick player-agreeable voting system to reset score and change levels <br></li><li>Minimalist look and feel lets you focus on what really matters: scrashing!</li></ul>",
