onsive, tight and fast-paced gameplay<br></li><li>7 Tailor-made levels to ensure the best experience after each score<br></li><li>Quick player-agreeable voting system to reset score and change levels <br></li><li>Minimalist look and feel lets you focus on what really matters: scrashing!</li></ul>",
